          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "In loving memory, from their sons, Arbeni and Genti.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 24.346
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "We love you MOM and DAD, forever.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 16.658
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "May you rest in peace, our guardian angels.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 16.059
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "Fill not your hearts with pain and sorrow, but remember me in every tomorrow.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 15.715
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-27",
        "text": "As long as I have the love of each of you, I can live in the hearts of all of you.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 15.775
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-29",
        "text": "Nenes dhe Babes tone to dashur",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 18.83
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-31",
        "text": "So dry your eyes and remember me, not as I am now, but as I used to be.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 16.001
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-32",
        "text": "Because, I will remember you all and look on with a smile.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 16.219
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-33",
        "text": "Understand in your hearts, I&apos;ve only gone to rest a little while.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 15.948
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-25",
        "text": "Remember the joy, the laughter, the smiles, I&apos;ve only gone to rest for a little while.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 15.602
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "I&apos;m you and you are me, and for as long as I breathe, you&apos;ll be with me.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 16.241
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 0
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      }
    ],
